query:
SELECT f.id, f.propertyId, f.userId, u.name, p.id as actual_property_id, p.address, p.county, p.parcelId 
FROM favorites f 
JOIN users u ON f.userId = u.id 
LEFT JOIN properties p ON f.propertyId = p.id
